Here is a backend design for FSAD‑PS41 that pairs with your React frontend, using Node.js + Express + MongoDB (you can adapt this for Spring Boot if needed).

1. Tech stack (backend)
Framework: Node.js + Express (REST API).

Database: MongoDB (via Mongoose) for User, Workshop, Session, Registration, Material.

Auth: JWT for login/session management.

Hosting: Run locally or deploy on Render/Heroku.

